io.gearpump.streaming.metrics

Class ProcessorAggregator.MultiLayerMap<Value>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.gearpump.streaming.metrics.ProcessorAggregator.MultiLayerMap<Value>
  • Enclosing class:
    ProcessorAggregator

    public static class ProcessorAggregator.MultiLayerMap<Value>
extends java.lang.Object
    MultiLayerMap has multiple layers. For each layer, there is a hashMap.

    To access a value with get, user need to specify first layer Id, then key.

    This class is optimized for performance.
